\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":47,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/09\/28\/believers-structure\/","url_meta":{"origin":2037,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: Believers are bricks supporting each other","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa\u00a0reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the believers are like bricks of a building, each part strengthening the other,\" and the Prophet\u00a0clasped his fingers together. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 481, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2585 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/18\/no-mercy-unless-show-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":2037,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah is not merciful to the unmerciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah will not be merciful to those who are not merciful to people.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7376, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2319 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":""